These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, august
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, romance
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, purple
City: marseilles, liverpool
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, drawing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Birthday      | august | january   |
| Movie-Genre          | musical     | romance |
| Color           | purple  | pink    |
| City   | liverpool  | marseilles    |
| Hobby           | hiking     | drawing   |
| Flower         | rose | poppy     |

