.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, amber
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, july
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, action
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, manager
1. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
4. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Color      | aquamarine      | amber   |
| Sport          | skateboarding     | golf    |
| Flower   | rose   | tulip        |
| Birthday   | july    | june      |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts  | action |
| Job     | dancer | manager       |

