2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the colombian is the person drinking coffee##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |
